Rocket sight for the Czech L-39 Albatros in the Russian air tree. Works with S-5k rockets in either 2 or 4 pod configurations. Gyroscopic and fixed versions of the sight are available, however I recommend the fixed sight due to how custom Gyros are handled by the game engine.
